he subagents are configured to log their actions to the system logs. In the meantime, I can check the journal for any related entries and report back that no activity was found, suggesting possible misconfigurations if that's unexpected.\n</","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/free","usage":{"input":11910,"output":1074,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12984,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772451215363}}
